 strives to be a virtual meeting point for discussion of this complex, fast-changing democracy – its politics, economy, culture and everyday life.</p><ul class="refer odd"><li><a href="http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/09/08/welcome-to-india-ink/" title="More about the blog »">More about the blog »</a></li><li><a href="mailto:indiaink@nytimes.com" title="E-mail the editors">E-mail the editors »</a></li></ul><ul class="refer even"><li><a href="http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/our-writers/">Our writers »</a></li><li><a href="http://twitter.com/nytindia" title="Follow us on Twitter">Follow us on Twitter »</a></li></ul></div></div><div id="archive" class="box module"><div class="entry"><h4>Archive</h4> <select name="archive_chrono" onchange="window.location.href=this.value; this.selectedIndex=this.options[0]"><option class="archiveform_option" value="">Select Month</option><option value='http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/'> January 2012</option><option value='http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/12/'> December 2011</option><option value='http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/11/'> November 2011</option><option value='http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/10/'> October 2011</option><option value='http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/09/'> September 2011</option> </select></div></div><div id="recent-posts" class="box module"><h4>Recent Posts</h4><div class='entry'><p class='date'>January 17<br /> <a class="post-comment hidden comment-number-only no-comment-prompt" href="http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/17/the-great-yoga-divide/"></a></p><h5><a href='http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/17/the-great-yoga-divide/' title='Read: The Great Yoga Divide'>The Great Yoga Divide</a></h5><p class='summary'> A recent controversy highlights how far Western yoga has moved from its traditional roots.</p></div><div class='entry'><p class='date'>January 17<br /> <a class="post-comment hidden comment-number-only no-comment-prompt" href="http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/17/hasi